room_title: Escape room "Mr. Dupree’s Office" by Escape LOU in Louisville
room_description: You are on an elite team of fellow CIA agents assigned with the task of gathering incriminating evidence from the office of an international businessman, Mr. Dupree. Our Intelligence team could only get you into Mr. Dupree’s office for 60 minutes. You must get out before Mr. Dupree returns or the case is blown!
